<i>noun</i>: 편도선염 [편도선념] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>편도선염 [편도선념]</dt><br>
<dd>tonsillitis</dd><br>
<dd>편도선에 염증이 생겨 열이 나고 편도선이 부어 음식을 삼키기 어려운 증상.</dd><br>
<dd>An inflammation of one's tonsils, whose symptoms include fever, swollen tonsils, and difficulty swallowing.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>